				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {CuInSe}_2$$\end{document} heterojunction that led to increased efficiency to 5.7%, exhibiting a short-circuit current density of about 31mA/cm2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
