				\begin{document}$$31 \,\hbox {mA}/\hbox {cm}^2$$\end{document}. During the 1980s, Potter et al., by introducing Zn0 in conjunction with p-type CuInSe2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
